  "content": [
    {
      "chapterUid": 47,
      "chapterTitle": "第四章 发动继续革命",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "3300030576_47_39512-39607",
          "range": "39512-39607",
          "rangeStart": 39512,
          "rangeEnd": 39607,
          "markText": "经验证明，封闭的国度是激进思潮和个人崇拜生长最适宜的土壤。而高度政治化的社会体制，使政治上的竞争成为向上流动唯一可能的途径，因而政治运动从来不缺乏积极分子，历次运动都造就了大批运动积极分子。",
          "colorStyle": 1,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1691410600,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2023-08-07 20:16:40",
          "chapterUid": 47,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300030576&chapterUid=47&rangeStart=39512&rangeEnd=39607",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/55032c80813ab7271g01603a?chapterUid=47&rangeStart=39512&rangeEnd=39607"
        },
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "3300030576_47_29595-29626",
          "range": "29595-29626",
          "rangeStart": 29595,
          "rangeEnd": 29626,
          "markText": "人类历史上的许多人为灾难，往往都宣称为了某种崇高的理想和目标。",
          "colorStyle": 1,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1691410577,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2023-08-07 20:16:17",
          "chapterUid": 47,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300030576&chapterUid=47&rangeStart=29595&rangeEnd=29626",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/55032c80813ab7271g01603a?chapterUid=47&rangeStart=29595&rangeEnd=29626"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "chapterUid": 48,
      "chapterTitle": "第五章 转向改革开放",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "3300030576_48_414-475",
          "range": "414-475",
          "rangeStart": 414,
          "rangeEnd": 475,
          "markText": "中国的改革开放和社会转型，被认为是20世纪末发生的两个影响深远的事件之一，另一个事件是苏联社会主义阵营解体和国际冷战终结。",
          "colorStyle": 1,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1691410549,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2023-08-07 20:15:49",
          "chapterUid": 48,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300030576&chapterUid=48&rangeStart=414&rangeEnd=475",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/55032c80813ab7271g01603a?chapterUid=48&rangeStart=414&rangeEnd=475"
        },
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "3300030576_48_29990-30088",
          "range": "29989-30087",
          "rangeStart": 29989,
          "rangeEnd": 30087,
          "markText": "传统社会主义实行共产党高度集权的无产阶级专政，消灭私有制和市场作用，实行生产资料公有制、全面的计划经济和按劳分配，推行优先发展重工业的强制工业化，与之相适应，严密控制思想舆论，对外部世界基本封闭。",
          "colorStyle": 1,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1691410506,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2023-08-07 20:15:06",
          "chapterUid": 48,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300030576&chapterUid=48&rangeStart=29989&rangeEnd=30087",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/55032c80813ab7271g01603a?chapterUid=48&rangeStart=29989&rangeEnd=30087"
        },
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "3300030576_48_32035-32152",
          "range": "32034-32151",
          "rangeStart": 32034,
          "rangeEnd": 32151,
          "markText": "革命化带来平等观念，推动社会结构的重新整合，为深陷苦难的普罗大众提供了一种改变命运的机会和希望。然而，革命化的负面后果是激进主义的持续泛滥，“不断革命”成了革命后的持续主题，毛泽东时代的一系列“左”倾政策都带有革命战争年代的经验胎记。",
          "colorStyle": 1,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1691410487,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2023-08-07 20:14:47",
          "chapterUid": 48,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300030576&chapterUid=48&rangeStart=32034&rangeEnd=32151",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/55032c80813ab7271g01603a?chapterUid=48&rangeStart=32034&rangeEnd=32151"
        },
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "3300030576_48_40577-40643",
          "range": "40576-40642",
          "rangeStart": 40576,
          "rangeEnd": 40642,
          "markText": "如果说世界上有两个坏东西，那么，一个是贪婪的资本，一个是腐败的权力。还有比这更坏的，就是权力与资本的合谋与分账，即所谓权贵资本主义。",
          "colorStyle": 1,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1691410234,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2023-08-07 20:10:34",
          "chapterUid": 48,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300030576&chapterUid=48&rangeStart=40576&rangeEnd=40642",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/55032c80813ab7271g01603a?chapterUid=48&rangeStart=40576&rangeEnd=40642"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "chapterUid": 49,
      "chapterTitle": "附录",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "3300030576_49_3043-3111",
          "range": "3043-3111",
          "rangeStart": 3043,
          "rangeEnd": 3111,
          "markText": "我想再说一点自己的看法：历史是一个歪打正着的结果。从冬连的“中国社会主义路径的五次选择”说起，我想再补充一下，历史还是个将错就错的过程。",
          "colorStyle": 1,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1691410431,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2023-08-07 20:13:51",
          "chapterUid": 49,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300030576&chapterUid=49&rangeStart=3043&rangeEnd=3111",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/55032c80813ab7271g01603a?chapterUid=49&rangeStart=3043&rangeEnd=3111"
        },
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "3300030576_49_7022-7156",
          "range": "7022-7156",
          "rangeStart": 7022,
          "rangeEnd": 7156,
          "markText": "中国当前的问题是新的问题：在市场化中形成的没有节制的资本，在既有体制下的不受制约的权力，两者结合起来了。这是当前社会转型的最大障碍，它有着更强大的攫取社会财富的能力，甚至能把子孙粮都给吃光了，却没有维护社会公平的道德能力，缺乏应有的社会责任的担当和制度的自我平衡能力。",
          "colorStyle": 1,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1691410403,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2023-08-07 20:13:23",
          "chapterUid": 49,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300030576&chapterUid=49&rangeStart=7022&rangeEnd=7156",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/55032c80813ab7271g01603a?chapterUid=49&rangeStart=7022&rangeEnd=7156"
        },
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "3300030576_49_7809-7852",
          "range": "7809-7852",
          "rangeStart": 7809,
          "rangeEnd": 7852,
          "markText": "即使我们暂时解答不了这些大问题，形成不了共识，但提出问题、讨论问题，本身就是巨大创新。",
          "colorStyle": 1,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1691410394,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2023-08-07 20:13:14",
          "chapterUid": 49,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300030576&chapterUid=49&rangeStart=7809&rangeEnd=7852",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/55032c80813ab7271g01603a?chapterUid=49&rangeStart=7809&rangeEnd=7852"
        },
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "3300030576_49_10773-10831",
          "range": "10773-10831",
          "rangeStart": 10773,
          "rangeEnd": 10831,
          "markText": "因为历史的脉络就是线性发展的，它虽会分出枝蔓，也有岔路和支流，但要它易于理解，还必得按照承继、递进的样式来加以展示。",
          "colorStyle": 1,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1691410378,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2023-08-07 20:12:58",
          "chapterUid": 49,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300030576&chapterUid=49&rangeStart=10773&rangeEnd=10831",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/55032c80813ab7271g01603a?chapterUid=49&rangeStart=10773&rangeEnd=10831"
        },
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "3300030576_49_9770-9881",
          "range": "9770-9881",
          "rangeStart": 9770,
          "rangeEnd": 9881,
          "markText": "毛泽东最大的悲剧在于，他没有从体制改革入手，还是坚持少数人领导，用群众暴力的手段，采取极左方式搞大民主，来解决这个命题，最终是失败了。最有价值的，是他提出了这个命题——社会主义社会执政的共产党不能保证今后不走向和人民对立。",
          "colorStyle": 1,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1691410365,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2023-08-07 20:12:45",
          "chapterUid": 49,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300030576&chapterUid=49&rangeStart=9770&rangeEnd=9881",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/55032c80813ab7271g01603a?chapterUid=49&rangeStart=9770&rangeEnd=9881"
        },
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "3300030576_49_11088-11140",
          "range": "11088-11140",
          "rangeStart": 11088,
          "rangeEnd": 11140,
          "markText": "世上不缺张口就是大道理的人。但不考究史实，以想当然论事的大道理，不仅不能服人，而且会遗人以柄，见笑大方。",
          "colorStyle": 1,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1691410337,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2023-08-07 20:12:17",
          "chapterUid": 49,
